DESCRIPTION:<p>If you can't explain how your newsroom creates value for its
  audience in one sentence\, you're not alone — but it's costing you. Every 
 newsroom\, no matter how small\, needs a clear value proposition to develop
  a cohesive editorial\, audience\, and revenue strategy. Without one\, you'
 ll struggle to offer a consistent product\, stand out in a crowded space\, 
 and make a compelling case for support from readers\, funders\, and adverti
 sers.</p><p>In this session\, you'll work through a lean\, two-step process
  to identify what makes your newsroom distinct — giving you the strategic c
 larity to make better decisions about coverage\, revenue\, and growth.<br><
 br>Tiny News Collective is inviting you to a scheduled Zoom meeting.<br><br
